title: Jason La Canfora explains how Le'Veon Bell trade could go down (Football 09/26)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by CBS Sports NFL Insider Jason La Canfora to break down the latest news and notes around the NFL, including concerns about the Rob Gronkowski trade and the Patriots future as well as what will happen with Le'Veon Bell, whether he will play with the Steelers ever again and where he might end up being traded to, including a sleeper team that may or may not have just won the Super Bowl (yes the Eagles).
